title: Blac Chyna Flaunts Super Slim Post-Baby Bod, Is Only 11 Pounds Away From Her Goal Weight
text: Blac Chyna Flaunts Super Slim Post-Baby Bod, Is Only 11 Pounds Away From Her Goal Weight by Lynda Brendish 1:35 PM PDT, March 26, 2017 Photo: Getty Images Blac Chyna is rocking her post-baby body goals! After giving birth to baby Dream back in November, the Rob and Chyna star shared a video of her newly svelte look in a curve-hugging dress to Snapchat over the weekend. Chyna showed off her small waist and flat stomach in the video, before hopping on the scales to reveal her current weight -- 141 pounds -- just 11 pounds from her goal weight of 130. "192 to 141.6 … Goal 130 (11 pounds to go)," she captioned the video. A post shared by The Kardashians ☘️ (@blacchynarmy) on Mar 25, 2017 at 3:37pm PDT Earlier this month, the 28-year-old reality star attributed her "snap back" to eating less meat and waist training. A post shared by Blac Chyna (@blacchyna) on Mar 6, 2017 at 12:24pm PST Check out more of Chyna's impressive post-baby weight loss in this video. RELATED SLIDESHOW
